---
// Services Component - Servicios Especializados
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white" id="servicios">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Servicios Especializados</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Soluciones a medida para cada etapa de tu camino cultural.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <!-- Gestión -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">strategy</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Gestión</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Planificación integral y administración de recursos para el éxito de tu iniciativa.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Asesorías -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">partner_reports</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Asesorías</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Mentoría personalizada uno a uno para desbloquear el potencial de tu marca.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Docencia -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">history_edu</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Docencia</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Programas académicos de alto nivel orientados a la gestión cultural práctica.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Charlas Vocacionales -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group relative">
                <span class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[var(--secondary)] text-[8px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter">Nuevo</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">diversity_3</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Charlas Vocacionales</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Inspirando a las nuevas generaciones a ver el arte como un camino profesional viable.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Producción Cultural -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">movie_edit</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Producción Cultural</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Ejecución técnica integral para dar vida a tus proyectos artísticos.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">celebration</span>
                        Eventos
                    </span>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">movie</span>
                        Cine
                    </span>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">theater_comedy</span>
                        Teatro
                    </span>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">storefront</span>
                        Ferias
                    </span>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700 bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">festival</span>
                        Festivales
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Marketing Cultural -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-purple-200 hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all group">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">ads_click</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Marketing Cultural</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Estrategias de comunicación para conectar tu obra con la audiencia ideal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
